Producer produces the data and store in a storage area.
	if producer is trying to add and storage is full
	producer will wait to get free storage or item removed
Consumer takes the data from the storage area.
	if there is no item in the storage customer has to wait
	when the item is added consumer will process it.

Solution:
We can have simple Q with fixed capacity and multiple producers which keeps on adding put and multiple
consumers which keep on removing.